name: Prescriber Id Qualifier Code
description: This variable contains information regarding the type of prescriber identification number that was submitted on the original PDE data, as reported by the Part D sponsor on the PDE record submitted to CMS.

fhirMapping.derived: The eob.careTeam element, for this prescriber id qualifier code, will only be supplied if the Prescriber Id is populated and the Prescriber Id Qualifier Code = '01'
